lead_paragraph: WEISBERG--Ethel (Feins), of Engelwood, NJ on May 27th. Wife of the late Seymour Weisberg. Mother of Mitchell (Randie), Wendy Smolen, and Edward (Diane Metzger). Services at Mt. Hebron Cemetery, Flushing, NY on Sunday, May 29th at 11:30am. 1/3
